{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":825,"text":"Have you ever noticed\nwhen you ask someone to talk"},{"time":3200,"text":"about a change they're making\nfor the better in their personal lives,"},{"time":6560,"text":"they're often really energetic?"},{"time":9015,"text":"Whether it's training for a marathon,"},{"time":11520,"text":"picking up an old hobby,"},{"time":12800,"text":"or learning a new skill,"},{"time":14680,"text":"for most people,"},{"time":15960,"text":"self-transformation projects\noccupy a very positive emotional space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21720,"text":"Self-transformation is empowering,"},{"time":24200,"text":"energizing, even exhilarating."},{"time":26560,"text":"I mean just take a look\nat some of the titles of self-help books:"},{"time":30360,"text":"\"Awaken the Giant Within,\""},{"time":33080,"text":"\"Practicing the Power of Now,\""},{"time":35600,"text":"or here's a great one\nwe can all relate to,"},{"time":38080,"text":"\"You are a Badass:"},{"time":40320,"text":"How to Stop Doubting Your Greatness\nand Start Living an Awesome Life.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":45440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48040,"text":"When it comes to self-transformation,"},{"time":51240,"text":"you can't help but get\na sense of the excitement."},{"time":56840,"text":"But there's another type of transformation"},{"time":60040,"text":"that occupies a very different\nemotional space."},{"time":64080,"text":"The transformation of organizations."},{"time":67880,"text":"If you're like most people,"},{"time":69240,"text":"when you hear the words \"Our organization\nis going to start a transformation,\""},{"time":73640,"text":"you're thinking, \"Uh-oh.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":75426,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76600,"text":"\"Layoffs.\""},{"time":78800,"text":"The blood drains from your face,"},{"time":80760,"text":"your mind goes into overdrive,"},{"time":83640,"text":"frantically searching\nfor some place to run and hide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88120,"text":"Well, you can run,"},{"time":89640,"text":"but you really can't hide."},{"time":92040,"text":"Most of us spend\nthe majority of our waking hours"},{"time":95040,"text":"involved in organizations."},{"time":97040,"text":"And due to changes in globalization,"},{"time":100160,"text":"changes due to advances in technology"},{"time":102720,"text":"and other factors,"},{"time":104560,"text":"the reality is our organizations\nare constantly having to adapt."},{"time":110360,"text":"In fact,"},{"time":111600,"text":"I call this the era\nof \"always-on\" transformation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117400,"text":"When I shared this idea\nwith my wife Nicola,"},{"time":119680,"text":"she said, \"Always-on transformation?"},{"time":122840,"text":"That sounds exhausting.\""},{"time":125640,"text":"And that may be\nexactly what you're thinking --"},{"time":127960,"text":"and you would be right."},{"time":129560,"text":"Particularly if we continue to approach\nthe transformation of organizations"},{"time":134720,"text":"the way we always have been."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136920,"text":"But because we can't hide,"},{"time":139360,"text":"we need to sort out two things."},{"time":141080,"text":"First,"},{"time":142320,"text":"why is transformation so exhausting?"},{"time":145080,"text":"And second, how do we fix it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":149200,"text":"First of all,"},{"time":150440,"text":"let's acknowledge that change is hard."},{"time":153600,"text":"People naturally resist change,"},{"time":155640,"text":"especially when it's imposed on them."},{"time":159200,"text":"But there are things that organizations do\nthat make change even harder"},{"time":163800,"text":"and more exhausting\nfor people than it needs to be."},{"time":167720,"text":"First of all,"},{"time":168960,"text":"leaders often wait too long to act."},{"time":173040,"text":"As a result,"},{"time":174280,"text":"everything is happening in crisis mode."},{"time":178320,"text":"Which, of course, tends to be exhausting."},{"time":181360,"text":"Or, given the urgency,"},{"time":184480,"text":"what they'll do is they'll just focus\non the short-term results,"},{"time":189320,"text":"but that doesn't give\nany hope for the future."},{"time":192560,"text":"Or they'll just take\na superficial, one-off approach,"},{"time":197040,"text":"hoping that they can return\nback to business as usual"},{"time":201160,"text":"as soon as the crisis is over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205600,"text":"This kind of approach"},{"time":206840,"text":"is kind of the way some students\napproach preparing for standardized tests."},{"time":214280,"text":"In order to get test scores to go up,"},{"time":217760,"text":"teachers will end up teaching to the test."},{"time":221160,"text":"Now, that approach can work;"},{"time":222560,"text":"test results often do go up."},{"time":224520,"text":"But it fails the fundamental\ngoal of education:"},{"time":228320,"text":"to prepare students\nto succeed over the long term."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234680,"text":"So given these obstacles,"},{"time":238160,"text":"what can we do"},{"time":240000,"text":"to transform the way\nwe transform organizations"},{"time":243480,"text":"so rather than being exhausting,"},{"time":246200,"text":"it's actually empowering and energizing?"},{"time":250160,"text":"To do that, we need to focus\non five strategic imperatives,"},{"time":255200,"text":"all of which have one thing in common:"},{"time":257959,"text":"putting people first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261079,"text":"The first imperative\nfor putting people first"},{"time":263760,"text":"is to inspire through purpose."},{"time":266120,"text":"Most transformations have\nfinancial and operational goals."},{"time":269840,"text":"These are important\nand they can be energizing to leaders,"},{"time":274120,"text":"but they tend not to be very motivating\nto most people in the organization."},{"time":278480,"text":"To motivate more broadly,"},{"time":280280,"text":"the transformation needs to connect\nwith a deeper sense of purpose."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285720,"text":"Take LEGO."},{"time":287640,"text":"The LEGO Group has become\nan extraordinary global company."},{"time":292520,"text":"Under their very capable leadership,"},{"time":294280,"text":"they've actually undergone\na series of transformations."},{"time":297800,"text":"While each of these\nhas had a very specific focus,"},{"time":301040,"text":"the North Star,"},{"time":302360,"text":"linking and guiding all of them,"},{"time":304200,"text":"has been Lego's powerful purpose:"},{"time":307480,"text":"inspire and develop\nthe builders of tomorrow."},{"time":312360,"text":"Expanding globally?"},{"time":314160,"text":"It's not about increasing sales,"},{"time":316600,"text":"but about giving millions of additional\nchildren access to LEGO building bricks."},{"time":321960,"text":"Investment and innovation?"},{"time":323960,"text":"It's not about developing new products,"},{"time":326360,"text":"but about enabling more children"},{"time":328680,"text":"to experience the joy\nof learning through play."},{"time":333440,"text":"Not surprisingly,"},{"time":335000,"text":"that deep sense of purpose tends\nto be highly motivating to LEGO's people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342120,"text":"The second imperative\nfor putting people first"},{"time":345080,"text":"is to go all in."},{"time":348080,"text":"Too many transformations"},{"time":349800,"text":"are nothing more than\nhead-count cutting exercises;"},{"time":353560,"text":"layoffs under the guise of transformation."},{"time":357960,"text":"In the face of relentless competition,"},{"time":360040,"text":"it may well be that you will\nhave to take the painful decision"},{"time":364000,"text":"to downsize the organization,"},{"time":366880,"text":"just as you may have to lose some weight\nin order to run a marathon."},{"time":372000,"text":"But losing weight alone"},{"time":373240,"text":"will not get you across\nthe finish line with a winning time."},{"time":376560,"text":"To win"},{"time":378160,"text":"you need to go all in."},{"time":380880,"text":"You need to go all in."},{"time":385160,"text":"Rather than just cutting costs,"},{"time":387640,"text":"you need to think about initiatives"},{"time":390200,"text":"that will enable you\nto win in the medium term,"},{"time":392920,"text":"initiatives to drive growth,"},{"time":394920,"text":"actions that will fundamentally\nchange the way the company operates,"},{"time":399000,"text":"and very importantly,"},{"time":400560,"text":"investments to develop\nthe leadership and the talent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406680,"text":"The third imperative\nfor putting people first"},{"time":410480,"text":"is to enable people with the capabilities"},{"time":413200,"text":"that they need to succeed\nduring the transformation and beyond."},{"time":420280,"text":"Over the years I've competed\nin a number of triathlons."},{"time":424280,"text":"You know, frankly, I'm not that good,"},{"time":426480,"text":"but I do have one distinct capability;"},{"time":430520,"text":"I am remarkably fast at finding my bike."}]},{"cues":[{"time":434640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":436560,"text":"By the time I finish the swim,"},{"time":438400,"text":"almost all the bikes are already gone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":444160,"text":"Real triathletes know that each leg --"},{"time":448240,"text":"the swim, the bike, the run --"},{"time":450000,"text":"really requires different capabilities,"},{"time":452520,"text":"different tools,"},{"time":453760,"text":"different skills, different techniques."},{"time":456440,"text":"Likewise when we transform organizations,"},{"time":458920,"text":"we need to be sure\nthat we're giving our people"},{"time":461800,"text":"the skills and the tools\nthey need along the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466160,"text":"Chronos,"},{"time":467400,"text":"a global software company,"},{"time":469400,"text":"recognized the need\nto transfer from building products --"},{"time":474360,"text":"software products --"},{"time":476040,"text":"to building software as a service."},{"time":479800,"text":"To enable its people\nto take that transformation,"},{"time":483040,"text":"first of all they invested in new tools"},{"time":485760,"text":"that would enable their employees\nto monitor the usage of the features"},{"time":490840,"text":"as well as customer satisfaction\nwith the new service."},{"time":494280,"text":"They also invested in skill development,"},{"time":498000,"text":"so that their employees would be able"},{"time":499840,"text":"to resolve customer service\nproblems on the spot."},{"time":502960,"text":"And very importantly,"},{"time":504200,"text":"they also reinforced the collaborative\nbehaviors that would be required"},{"time":507600,"text":"to deliver an end-to-end\nseamless customer experience."},{"time":512679,"text":"Because of these investments,"},{"time":514280,"text":"rather than feeling overwhelmed\nby the transformation,"},{"time":517640,"text":"Chronos employees actually felt energized"},{"time":520919,"text":"and empowered in their new roles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524200,"text":"In the era of \"always-on\" transformation,"},{"time":526440,"text":"change is a constant."},{"time":527960,"text":"My fourth imperative therefore"},{"time":529920,"text":"is to instill a culture\nof continuous learning."},{"time":534800,"text":"When Satya Nadella\nbecame the CEO of Microsoft"},{"time":537840,"text":"in February 2014,"},{"time":539800,"text":"he embarked on an ambitious\ntransformation journey"},{"time":542720,"text":"to prepare the company to compete\nin a mobile-first, cloud-first world."},{"time":547640,"text":"This included changes to strategy,"},{"time":549960,"text":"the organization"},{"time":551200,"text":"and very importantly, the culture."},{"time":554280,"text":"Microsoft's culture at the time was one\nof silos and internal competition --"},{"time":559320,"text":"not exactly conducive to learning."},{"time":562480,"text":"Nadella took this head-on."},{"time":565560,"text":"He rallied his leadership\naround his vision"},{"time":569000,"text":"for a living, learning culture,"},{"time":572240,"text":"shifting from a fixed mindset,"},{"time":574600,"text":"where your role was to show up\nas the smartest person in the room,"},{"time":578000,"text":"to a growth mindset,"},{"time":579840,"text":"where your role was to listen, to learn\nand to bring out the best in people."},{"time":586720,"text":"Well, early days,"},{"time":588000,"text":"Microsoft employees already\nnoticed this shift in the culture --"},{"time":592080,"text":"clear evidence of Microsoft\nputting people first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596560,"text":"My fifth and final imperative\nis specifically for leaders."},{"time":601200,"text":"In a transformation,"},{"time":602880,"text":"a leader needs to have a vision,"},{"time":605160,"text":"a clear road map with milestones,"},{"time":608600,"text":"and then you need to hold people\naccountable for results."},{"time":613080,"text":"In other words, you need to be directive."},{"time":616240,"text":"But in order to capture\nthe hearts and minds of people,"},{"time":619400,"text":"you also need to be inclusive."},{"time":622680,"text":"Inclusive leadership\nis critical to putting people first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":627920,"text":"I live in the San Francisco Bay area."},{"time":630680,"text":"And right now,"},{"time":631920,"text":"our basketball team\nis the best in the league."},{"time":634960,"text":"We won the 2015 championship,"},{"time":637640,"text":"and we're favored to win again this year."},{"time":640600,"text":"There are many explanations for this."},{"time":642680,"text":"They have some fabulous players,"},{"time":645120,"text":"but one of the key reasons"},{"time":646920,"text":"is their head coach, Steve Kerr,\nis an inclusive leader."},{"time":653360,"text":"When Kerr came to the Warriors in 2014,"},{"time":656000,"text":"the Warriors were looking\nfor a major transformation."},{"time":659480,"text":"They hadn't won a national\nchampionship since 1975."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665640,"text":"Kerr came in, and he had a clear vision,"},{"time":668840,"text":"and he immediately got to work."},{"time":672480,"text":"From the outset,"},{"time":673840,"text":"he reached out and engaged\nthe players and the staff."},{"time":677960,"text":"He created an environment of open debate\nand solicited suggestions."},{"time":683360,"text":"During games he would often ask,"},{"time":685080,"text":"\"What are you seeing that I'm missing?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":688000,"text":"One the best examples of this\ncame in game four of the 2015 finals."},{"time":694600,"text":"The Warriors were down two games to one"},{"time":697880,"text":"when Kerr made the decision\nto change the starting lineup;"},{"time":702600,"text":"a bold move by any measure."},{"time":707360,"text":"The Warriors won the game\nand went on to win the championship."},{"time":710960,"text":"And it is widely viewed"},{"time":712240,"text":"that that move was\nthe pivotal move in their victory."}]},{"cues":[{"time":717440,"text":"Interestingly, it wasn't\nactually Kerr's idea."},{"time":722560,"text":"It was the idea of his 28-year-old\nassistant, Nick U'Ren."},{"time":727160,"text":"Because of Kerr's leadership style,"},{"time":729360,"text":"U'Ren felt comfortable\nbringing the idea forward."},{"time":733240,"text":"And Kerr not only listened,"},{"time":735240,"text":"but he implemented the idea"},{"time":737520,"text":"and then afterwards,"},{"time":739200,"text":"gave U'Ren all the credit --"},{"time":742520,"text":"actions all consistent with Kerr's\nhighly inclusive approach to leadership."}]},{"cues":[{"time":749280,"text":"In the era of \"always-on\" transformation,"},{"time":751960,"text":"organizations are always\ngoing to be transforming."},{"time":757200,"text":"But doing so does not\nhave to be exhausting."},{"time":762080,"text":"We owe it to ourselves,"},{"time":764280,"text":"to our organizations"},{"time":766280,"text":"and to society more broadly"},{"time":769000,"text":"to boldly transform\nour approach to transformation."},{"time":773920,"text":"To do that,"},{"time":775600,"text":"we need to start putting people first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":779800,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":781040,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}